    them safe to use without asking
    for permission or giving credit to the artist - even for commercial purposes. Below are the media sources:
    <ul>
        <li><a href="https://pixabay.com/" target="_new">pixabay.com</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://unsplash.com/" target="_new">unsplash.com</a></li>
